reviewText: The item arrived promptly and well packaged. What a great VHS on the Elizabeth Bowes-Lyons, The Duchess of York, Queen Elizabeth, and Qeen Mum.  Great pictures, and vintage film of a great royal lady during the many transitions of her life.  I enjoyed it tremendously!
A great collection of facts and pictures about the life of Queen Elizabeth, the Queen Mother. It was done at the time of her 90th birthday and showed the many facets of this great lady.
